longBusinessSummary: Ying Li International Real Estate Limited, an investment holding company, operates as a property developer in Singapore, Hong Kong, and the People's Republic of China. It operates through Property Development and Property Investment segments. The company primarily develops office, retail, car park, and other projects. It is also involved in the provision of property consulting, selling, marketing, and leasing services, as well as mall and property management, and corporate management consultancy services. The company was incorporated in 1991 and is headquartered in Singapore. Ying Li International Real Estate Limited is a subsidiary of State Alpha Limited.
